// $Id$

1 Introduction
======================================================================
This document is about listing the controls that are, or will be part
of canui, as well as their status.


2 Working controls
======================================================================
These control have enough basic functionality so that they may be
used. They may lack in options, callbacks or in ways to obtain
information.


button/checkbox/radio
  Todo: keyboard
  Bugs: none


combobox
  Todo: none
  Bugs: non


link
  Todo: none
  Bugs: non


panel
  Todo: none
  Bugs: none


progress
  Todo: none
  Bugs: none


status_bar
  Todo: this is currently just a panel. It will either be
        removed or reworked completely.
  Bugs: none


tooltip
  Todo: none
  Bugs:
   . tooltip stays stuck when mouse leaves (cancel timer on leave?)


separator
  Todo: none
  Bugs: none


image
  Todo: none
  Bugs: none


label
  Todo: none
  Bugs: none


scrollbar
  Todo: mouse wheel, keyboard
  Bugs: none


scroller
  Todo: mouse wheel, keyboard
  Bugs: problems with interaction between h and v while resizing stuff


slider
  Todo: keyboard
  Bugs: none


textbox
  Todo: dnd, undo/redo, scrolling
  Bugs: double-click select and moving sometimes unselect original
        word; multiline selection + replace sometimes corrupts content

dialog
  Todo: none
  Bugs: none


3 Controls in progress
======================================================================
These controls are currently mostly unusable because of lack of
testing or features, or bugs.

menu
  Todo: separators, keybindings?, icons, disabled, customize, close on
        click elsewhere, timers, checkboxes/radios

list
  Todo: column resize/move, item drag/drop, other views (icon, etc.),
        icon in column, allow any control (editable list), tooltips
  Bugs: sorting the list keeps the focus on the same index instead
        of following the item


